text: Politotdel () is a rural locality (a selo) in Shestayevsky Selsoviet, Davlekanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 191 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Davlekanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Davlekanovsky District
title: Politotdel, Republic of Bashkortostan
